This template assumes a hypothetical change where `com.example.Service.connect()` is replaced by `com.example.Service.connect(int timeout)`. It implements all the critical rules (Sniper Printer, NoClasspath safety, and Generic safety) and can be easily adapted to your specific diff once available.

